title: JRE #293 - Cara Santa Maria, Brian Redban [64k Time Warped]
description:
JRE #293 - Cara Santa Maria, Brian Redban [64k Time Warped]


This is the Joe Rogan Experience Podcast #293 64k Time Warped version. Time warped means the audio is played 38% faster but without changing the pitch. They just talk a lot faster =)
The reason behind this is to save time for the JRE junkies out there, you save about 50 minutes of your life on a 3 hour podcast. Aint that just great? Since its encoded with OGG aoTuVb q0 its also smaller in filesize and good quality.
